title: Inside Moebius, 2 tomes [FRENCH][CBR]
description:
Have a peak inside the head of this ground breaking artist. Meet Major Grubert, Arzach, and Blueberry smoking weed with their creator in his kitchen. In the narative style of his early shorts, Moebius takes us through his universe in a casual shorthand drawing style introducing us not only to his own creations, but also interacting with such great fictions as osama bin laden himself(!)

Two tomes in one.

Oh, and about the french, dont worry. 75% of this work is graphical, and you dont have to be a frenchman to understand whats going on. In fact, allthough youre french, you won't have a clue anyway :D
